Okay, let me add the PassInfo class. I am planning to just put the following info there:
```c++
class PassInfoNode : public RelayNode {
  std::string name;
  int opt_level;
  std::vector<std::string> required;
};
```
Then we probably need to have `PassInfo pass_info` in each subclass, and `SetPassInfo(PassInfo)` in the pass. `GetPassInfo` is probably not need as pass_info would be public.

Anything to add or remove?
